  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2546480/extras/ffc5b1d0158ebccd1b12ac110190f81c.avif?t=1764521700\" width=1536 height=1024 /></span>Keep it modest<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2546480/extras/fe20e96cdf8b73cf13d02f773eb17240.avif?t=1764521700\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2546480/extras_big/fe20e96cdf8b73cf13d02f773eb17240.webp?t=1764521700 width=1560 height=390 /></span>OR GO COMPLETELY WILD—YOUR CHOICE!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2546480/extras/30cf9889b62e8eb27b5d5587911324d9.avif?t=1764521700\" width=1560 height=695 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >During your journeys through various dimensions, you unexpectedly find yourself in an empty and mysterious interdimensional museum. The enigmatic director asks for your help in restoring it after a cataclysmic interdimensional collision that wiped it clean. He grants you the power to summon a magical spade, capable of digging through the sands of the Infinity Islets to unearth hidden interdimensional artifacts that could be literally anything, and a chain to bring them back to the museum safely. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Your goal is to return the artifacts you discover, create incredible exhibitions, and restore the museum to its former glory.</strong> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Dig. Discover. Collect. Create.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From robots to bananas, discover random interdimensional artifacts and craft exhibits limited only by your imagination.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bring the empty museum to life — it’s your canvas to shape.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2546480/extras/f299fc9ddc037b29fa0ce65d1d3a30f8.poster.avif?t=1764521700\" width=800 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2546480/extras/f299fc9ddc037b29fa0ce65d1d3a30f8.webm?t=1764521700\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2546480/extras/f299fc9ddc037b29fa0ce65d1d3a30f8.mp4?t=1764521700\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Write your own story—literally ✍️</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Edit artifact descriptions in any language. Choose a name for your cat—or your wolf!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Artifacts that play music and sounds 🎶</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Enhance the atmosphere with artifacts that play music from various genres and immersive sounds to bring your exhibition to life.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Help a wandering orb of light reach its destination and earn a reward ⚪</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But you’ll have to catch it first! Complete the new quest introduced in version 1.0.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Show off your exhibits! </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Share your save file and let friends explore your museum.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Glide across floating islets </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Glide across procedurally generated  islets and buildings—each one unique.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Seasonal events 🎃☃️🐣</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover unique artifacts available only during seasonal events.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2546480/extras/58724c49dd3f1be2e8004c806092ab98.poster.avif?t=1764521700\" width=798 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2546480/extras/58724c49dd3f1be2e8004c806092ab98.webm?t=1764521700\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2546480/extras/58724c49dd3f1be2e8004c806092ab98.mp4?t=1764521700\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2546480/extras/672716f6c3b0945756752b18885dbcfd.avif?t=1764521700\" width=1536 height=1024 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2546480/extras/0e0acceeecef7e96b7d142afac4f47eb.poster.avif?t=1764521700\" width=800 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2546480/extras/0e0acceeecef7e96b7d142afac4f47eb.webm?t=1764521700\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2546480/extras/0e0acceeecef7e96b7d142afac4f47eb.mp4?t=1764521700\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2546480/extras/ffc5b1d0158ebccd1b12ac110190f81c.avif?t=1764521700\" width=1536 height=1024 /></span>Keep it modest<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2546480/extras/fe20e96cdf8b73cf13d02f773eb17240.avif?t=1764521700\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2546480/extras_big/fe20e96cdf8b73cf13d02f773eb17240.webp?t=1764521700 width=1560 height=390 /></span>OR GO COMPLETELY WILD—YOUR CHOICE!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2546480/extras/30cf9889b62e8eb27b5d5587911324d9.avif?t=1764521700\" width=1560 height=695 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >During your journeys through various dimensions, you unexpectedly find yourself in an empty and mysterious interdimensional museum. The enigmatic director asks for your help in restoring it after a cataclysmic interdimensional collision that wiped it clean. He grants you the power to summon a magical spade, capable of digging through the sands of the Infinity Islets to unearth hidden interdimensional artifacts that could be literally anything, and a chain to bring them back to the museum safely. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Your goal is to return the artifacts you discover, create incredible exhibitions, and restore the museum to its former glory.</strong> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Dig. Discover. Collect. Create.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From robots to bananas, discover random interdimensional artifacts and craft exhibits limited only by your imagination.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bring the empty museum to life — it’s your canvas to shape.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2546480/extras/f299fc9ddc037b29fa0ce65d1d3a30f8.poster.avif?t=1764521700\" width=800 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2546480/extras/f299fc9ddc037b29fa0ce65d1d3a30f8.webm?t=1764521700\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2546480/extras/f299fc9ddc037b29fa0ce65d1d3a30f8.mp4?t=1764521700\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Write your own story—literally ✍️</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Edit artifact descriptions in any language. Choose a name for your cat—or your wolf!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Artifacts that play music and sounds 🎶</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Enhance the atmosphere with artifacts that play music from various genres and immersive sounds to bring your exhibition to life.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Help a wandering orb of light reach its destination and earn a reward ⚪</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But you’ll have to catch it first! Complete the new quest introduced in version 1.0.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Show off your exhibits! </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Share your save file and let friends explore your museum.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Glide across floating islets </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Glide across procedurally generated  islets and buildings—each one unique.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Seasonal events 🎃☃️🐣</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover unique artifacts available only during seasonal events.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2546480/extras/58724c49dd3f1be2e8004c806092ab98.poster.avif?t=1764521700\" width=798 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2546480/extras/58724c49dd3f1be2e8004c806092ab98.webm?t=1764521700\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2546480/extras/58724c49dd3f1be2e8004c806092ab98.mp4?t=1764521700\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2546480/extras/672716f6c3b0945756752b18885dbcfd.avif?t=1764521700\" width=1536 height=1024 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2546480/extras/0e0acceeecef7e96b7d142afac4f47eb.poster.avif?t=1764521700\" width=800 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2546480/extras/0e0acceeecef7e96b7d142afac4f47eb.webm?t=1764521700\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2546480/extras/0e0acceeecef7e96b7d142afac4f47eb.mp4?t=1764521700\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
